version_description:
Thank you for using the app! 
We fixed bugs and made some improvements to enhance your experience with the application.

What’s new in this version:
- Fixed crashes
- Improved overall application performance.
- Made it so that on all devices the application now looks equally cool
- UX improvements
We are still waiting for feedback from you for further product improvements!

Hey everybody!
We added Profile! Now you can check the test result, and make retest.
At the next week you are waiting new features. We work very hard and want to show you our development soon
Leave your feedbacks, it's will help me to do app better

We added new modes for volume boost!
Now you can switching between modes, and use it in the different places:
- In a car
- Cinema/ Theater
- Inside
- Outside
- Music
This modes is created individual for you, after your hear test. Try it and leave feedback

In this update:

- Auto-detect the output speaker when working without headphones.
- interface adaptation 5, 8, X
- Added new localizations
- Fixed noise when using the device
- UX improvements
- Fixed crashes
Leave your feedbacks!

Hey! We are worked hard and now we ready to show you what we did in this update:
- Improved connection with AirPods. Now you can connect AirPods in during session
- UX improvements
- Fixed crashes
Leave your feedbacks!
